{"tid":958090,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人聽過懷俄明州事件(Wyoming Incident)？","createTime":"2018-12-27T13:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T18:17:01.000Z","uid":17075,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bfb1d70e6bdcabb48031b02c5477e1881e090fd7","tid":958090,"uid":17075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:49:11.000Z","msg":"蘋果廣告單野咁多人討論，咁有冇人聽過呢單更加神秘嘅電視廣告？唔講咁多，去片先：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IBHkW0aKHRc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIBHkW0aKHRc&d=wP1V4d3dEokp1rN2RNzFfy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=f82eb33f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IBHkW0aKHRc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BmB3RhQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmB3RhQ.png&h=6f2db759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「都市傳說」又來了！這次發生的地點在美國「懷俄明州」(Wyoming)，由於整個過程太令人毛骨悚然，甚少有人直接提起，只敢稱之為「懷俄明州事件」(The Wyoming Incident)。也奉勸各位「晚上一個人的時候不要看喔.....！」 (影片內容可能令人不安，敬希注意)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1k6b0bn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1k6b0bn.png&h=db6b5977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n準備好了嗎？事情是這樣的，話說「懷俄明州事件」是在 1987 年美國「懷俄明州」一間電視台的一段新聞節目中發生，當時主播正要報導一則新聞時，電視廣播訊號突然受到干擾，在一陣雜訊過後，出現這段詭異的文字：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">333-333-333 We Present A SPECIAL PRESENTATION</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/piuH6RL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpiuH6RL.png&h=dc339d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這是「333-333-333 特別廣播」的意思，本來應該沒甚麼。但在一片死寂之後，背景竟漸漸響起陰沉的弦樂伴奏，接著又出現一串催眠般的文字「YOU WILL SEE SUCH PRETTY THINGS」(你會看見美麗的事物)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XHdt2qj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXHdt2qj.png&h=74a5644d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZLj85m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZLj85m.png&h=d95a4538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最恐怖的來了，音樂結束後，畫面上浮出一張貼近的人臉，然後在再一次的特別廣播字樣後，一陣音效暴響伴隨著接連出現的頭顱，並寫著「YOU ARE ILL」」、「WE JUST WANT TO FIX YOU」(你病了，我們想要修好你)......<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gpkDFca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgpkDFca.png&h=ae9d2d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這段意義不明的神秘廣播持續 6 分鐘左右，畫面最後又回到原本被切掉的新聞片段.....本來對於一些較大膽的人來說，覺得影片內容也不怎麼樣吧，最多是比較詭異而已......但事情當然不止這樣，有人表示看完後整天覺得心緒不寧，有人表示出現頭痛及噁心感覺，更有人表示腦裡經常出現一把聲音，久久揮之不去........有人懷疑是神秘組織向民眾洗腦等！<br />\n<br />\n究竟是真是假？「都市傳說」就是這樣，從來沒有確實答案！有人說，『這其實是一個 Alternate Reality Game (ARG) 的遊戲宣傳，也就是以真實世界為基礎，在媒體平台上述說一段故事的遊戲。故事當中就有一個神秘組織駭進了電視廣播，而插入他們自己的廣播......』....他似乎忘記了當時是 1987 年.....何來網上遊戲？forget it！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/27/214812_82740e0d6a241006b6b81b3f502d8ed4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F27%2F214812_82740e0d6a241006b6b81b3f502d8ed4.png&h=eec0f9ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是宣傳？是惡作劇？一切反應都是心理作用？<br />\n<br />\nBtw 原Po:<br />\n<a href=\"https://kason2047.pixnet.net/blog/post/263411059-%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E6%AF%9B%E9%AA%A8%E6%82%9A%E7%84%B6%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E6%87%B7%E4%BF%84%E6%98%8E%E5%B7%9E%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%8D%28%E8%A6%96%E9%A0%BB%29\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkason2047.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F263411059-%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AF%259B%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E6%2582%259A%25E7%2584%25B6%25E7%259A%2584%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2587%25B7%25E4%25BF%2584%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B7%259E%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E3%2580%258D%2528%25E8%25A6%2596%25E9%25A0%25BB%2529&d=wP1V4d3dEokp1rN2RNzFfy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c2025055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kason2047.pixnet.net/blog/post/263411059-%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E6%AF%9B%E9%AA%A8%E6%82%9A%E7%84%B6%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8C%E6%87%B7%E4%BF%84%E6%98%8E%E5%B7%9E%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%8D%28%E8%A6%96%E9%A0%BB%29</a><br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢單仲神秘過蘋果廣告製作囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff807e241d8542d93e5ad17272d6a9273ca5f04a","tid":958090,"uid":17075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:52:10.000Z","msg":"個奇怪廣告會比較耐，大家比較耐性去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0754d0df742b7814e0c8a4880e52e690f30fcb","tid":958090,"uid":5205,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"慎入啦屌你"},{"pid":"b974ea5b05cd0e8a01e28e63b114a5904bd539ab","tid":958090,"uid":23416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0754d0df742b7814e0c8a4880e52e690f30fcb","tid":958090,"uid":5205,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"慎入啦屌你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T18:16:24.000Z","msg":"咁都好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8c4bd3f8d992f46275c7929b7945dc59853b7a","tid":958090,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b974ea5b05cd0e8a01e28e63b114a5904bd539ab","tid":958090,"uid":23416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0754d0df742b7814e0c8a4880e52e690f30fcb","tid":958090,"uid":5205,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"慎入啦屌你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T18:16:24.000Z","msg":"咁都好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T18:17:01.000Z","msg":"驚咪驚 個啲黑白圖人樣我好撚驚"}]}